{"tid":1803204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建制坐定定都贏","createTime":"2019-12-30T04:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T05:32:57.000Z","uid":175340,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88955cd9daca414bed2ab2fc7feb7b0b65a7996a","tid":1803204,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"下個月7號就選區主席<br />\n以下係北區席位分佈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>素人：7席<br />\n民主黨：5席<br />\n新同盟：3席<br />\n工聯會：1席<br />\n民建聯：1席<br />\n鄉事：1席</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n正常黃藍陣營既話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇可能會輸</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但北區係唯一一區素人議席多過泛民<br />\n下面樓豬話 <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">班素人「乳臭未乾」<br />\n未坐好就諗住做大佬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地夠唔夠資格我唔知<br />\n我只係知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃營繼續內鬥嘅話<br />\n建制又可以食花生分餅了</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光咩復香港<br />\n目標都唔一致</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生生性性啦屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n補返link:<br />\n<br />\n北區連線你班仆街，夠膽就支持建制派做主席，下屆區選一定唔支持你地！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787380</a>"},{"pid":"a88e78a12bc64c574ac4baedddc9c939f3ee7852","tid":1803204,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n目標一致 push 1/10"},{"pid":"92c431f22c93e0e7e1797f3e455d5eb600ac78c4","tid":1803204,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n目標一致 push 2/10"},{"pid":"3b2a5a13311edb772492e7476d8